WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: 9vZou--5UEo

NOTE Language: en

00:02:42.700 --> 00:02:46.770
What I was telling them,

00:02:47.198 --> 00:02:51.937
the way you are celebrating My birthday,

00:02:52.137 --> 00:02:55.254
I’m overjoyed

00:02:55.454 --> 00:03:01.179
and I don’t know how to express that joy

00:03:01.379 --> 00:03:05.258
which is really overflowing.

00:03:07.677 --> 00:03:12.199
I really don’t know what have I done for you

00:03:13.549 --> 00:03:16.491
that you have come up

00:03:16.691 --> 00:03:23.137
with such enthusiasm, with such love.

00:03:25.173 --> 00:03:36.333
It’s your great heart which is appreciating My humble work.

00:03:41.985 --> 00:03:47.989
All over the world, Sahaja Yoga has spread

00:03:48.189 --> 00:03:52.486
and again spreading like fire.

00:03:52.686 --> 00:03:59.010
That showed it was the need of the world.

00:03:59.210 --> 00:04:02.740
It was the need of the people.

00:04:02.940 --> 00:04:12.799
That’s why they have taken to Sahaj Yog with such enthusiasm.

00:04:18.522 --> 00:04:23.864
I could understand in a country like India,

00:04:24.375 --> 00:04:28.777
where they have talked about Self Realization,

00:04:29.804 --> 00:04:38.866
but in a country which is not aware of a higher spiritual life,

00:04:39.974 --> 00:04:48.091
you all should appreciate, assimilate and enjoy Sahaja Yoga

00:04:48.758 --> 00:04:55.608
as a very great blessing of the times.

00:04:56.055 --> 00:05:00.435
These are special times, I think

00:05:02.831 --> 00:05:17.435
that you have fallen into this trap of love and enlightenment.

00:05:21.622 --> 00:05:36.148
I Myself was not very sure that you would appreciate the love

00:05:39.212 --> 00:05:45.191
that one can enjoy within yourself.

00:05:45.801 --> 00:05:51.039
What is a spiritual understanding?

00:05:52.140 --> 00:06:02.068
I didn’t know how you would appreciate and enjoy yourself.

00:06:03.127 --> 00:06:09.695
That means you are all very much capable of this tremendous love

00:06:09.895 --> 00:06:13.297
and this spiritual awakening.

00:06:13.497 --> 00:06:16.340
No doubt about it.

00:06:16.540 --> 00:06:22.470
How is it it has worked out so beautifully?

00:06:23.284 --> 00:06:30.562
Very surprising and also

00:06:30.762 --> 00:06:36.517
the way you have got your spiritual powers

00:06:36.747 --> 00:06:40.468
and the way you are using it

00:06:40.668 --> 00:06:48.170
is really beyond understanding, any human understanding.

00:06:48.370 --> 00:06:51.479
That’s why people don’t believe

00:06:51.679 --> 00:06:55.733
that there’s something like Sahaj Yog,

00:06:55.933 --> 00:07:01.711
that there is a power in every human being

00:07:01.911 --> 00:07:08.224
which is universal and which can be enlightened.

00:07:09.634 --> 00:07:17.539
It’s something beyond the conception of human beings

00:07:18.996 --> 00:07:22.316
that they can achieve this kind

00:07:22.516 --> 00:07:27.213
of a spiritual growth within themselves.

00:07:30.071 --> 00:07:34.978
I wonder how many of you also realize

00:07:36.705 --> 00:07:41.383
that whatever you have achieved is something great.

00:07:44.520 --> 00:07:55.747
It is the climax of human development, human growth

00:07:55.947 --> 00:08:00.705
and all the advancement we have made.

00:08:03.434 --> 00:08:06.359
This will change,

00:08:06.559 --> 00:08:14.701
definitely change the world and its understanding.

00:08:16.845 --> 00:08:21.495
I’m talking to you today at the time

00:08:21.695 --> 00:08:35.024
when the war of Iraq is on in a very big way.

00:08:35.711 --> 00:08:43.413
I don’t know what to say, how it is going to work out,

00:08:44.826 --> 00:08:49.972
but with all your efforts towards peace,

00:08:50.172 --> 00:09:00.234
it will get solved I’m sure and will bring peace everywhere.

00:09:12.312 --> 00:09:16.204
We don’t want to have wars,

00:09:18.296 --> 00:09:22.059
but we have to change human beings,

00:09:22.259 --> 00:09:26.650
otherwise you cannot trust them.

00:09:26.850 --> 00:09:31.352
This is a very big challenge to all of you.

00:09:31.552 --> 00:09:35.400
You have to work very hard

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:48.686
to get to this idea of giving Realization to everyone,

00:09:51.095 --> 00:09:54.336
otherwise you cannot stop it

00:09:54.536 --> 00:10:01.395
just by giving them lectures or threatening them.

00:10:03.393 --> 00:10:08.139
The awakening is needed within, which, of course,

00:10:08.339 --> 00:10:12.321
I don’t know if everyone will try to have.

00:10:12.521 --> 00:10:15.820
But, as many as can have it,

00:10:16.077 --> 00:10:21.318
please try to give them awakening

00:10:21.856 --> 00:10:25.913
because they are all human beings

00:10:26.113 --> 00:10:33.176
born at this time and so they deserve it.

00:10:33.412 --> 00:10:36.433
You have to just try

00:10:36.683 --> 00:10:40.437
meeting them, talking to them

00:10:41.455 --> 00:10:47.027
and giving them Self Realization.

00:10:47.227 --> 00:10:54.561
It’s not very difficult. Every one of you can do that.

00:10:54.948 --> 00:11:01.301
Every one of you have only ten to fifteen people

00:11:01.501 --> 00:11:05.360
and will change the world.

00:11:05.560 --> 00:11:13.015
That is our ambition, is to change the world

00:11:14.075 --> 00:11:19.770
to the new style of understanding

00:11:19.970 --> 00:11:26.048
that we have to live peacefully as human beings.

00:11:26.248 --> 00:11:29.977
Without any discretion of color,

00:11:30.177 --> 00:11:35.466
without any discretion of nations,

00:11:35.891 --> 00:11:40.775
we all have to live together as human beings.

00:11:40.975 --> 00:11:47.525
This is the only difference between human beings and animals.

00:11:47.725 --> 00:11:53.639
As long as we are not spiritual, it’s all right.

00:11:53.839 --> 00:11:59.245
But if you can transform them into spiritual personalities,

00:11:59.445 --> 00:12:02.707
I’m sure everything will change.

00:12:02.907 --> 00:12:06.896
As we have seen now in Sahaja Yoga,

00:12:07.096 --> 00:12:16.212
it doesn’t bother a Sahaja Yogi to quarrel or to fight,

00:12:16.412 --> 00:12:21.033
but they are so peaceful and gentle with each other.

00:12:21.820 --> 00:12:25.440
So today we have to pray

00:12:25.640 --> 00:12:30.465
that Sahaja Yoga must spread all over the world

00:12:30.665 --> 00:12:38.131
and that everyone in the world should get realized.

00:12:38.331 --> 00:12:43.849
You have to promise that you will go out of the way

00:12:44.049 --> 00:12:55.104
and try to change the human beings

00:12:56.717 --> 00:13:03.413
who are just mislaid on their way somewhere.

00:13:05.359 --> 00:13:12.588
I’m sure once it starts working out,

00:13:12.788 --> 00:13:15.469
everybody will understand

00:13:15.669 --> 00:13:21.580
the value of peaceful life as Sahaja Yogis.

00:13:26.924 --> 00:13:30.795
We have to do intensive work

00:13:34.726 --> 00:13:42.071
because you can see human beings needed this.

00:13:42.271 --> 00:13:46.368
Today that is the need of the hour.

00:13:48.915 --> 00:13:57.998
At the right time, we are now ready to do Sahaj Yog

00:13:58.661 --> 00:14:04.576
and spread it all over, as much as possible,

00:14:05.162 --> 00:14:10.631
wherever you will see the necessity.

00:14:12.862 --> 00:14:18.036
Of course, it will work, but otherwise also,

00:14:18.236 --> 00:14:21.852
whether there is necessity or not,

00:14:22.052 --> 00:14:28.792
there’s an urge in the human beings to rise,

00:14:28.992 --> 00:14:35.398
rise above all these human failures.

00:14:36.387 --> 00:14:40.136
I bless you from My heart,

00:14:43.257 --> 00:14:46.246
bless you very much,

00:14:46.446 --> 00:14:50.121
that you carry on your work

00:14:50.321 --> 00:14:53.389
of Sahaja Yoga, of spreading Sahaja Yoga,

00:14:53.589 --> 00:14:56.093
of giving Realization.

00:14:56.293 --> 00:14:59.412
You have got powers.

00:14:59.657 --> 00:15:01.859
You know you have.

00:15:02.059 --> 00:15:10.177
Only use that power and give Realization to people.

00:15:11.153 --> 00:15:17.831
That is one promise you have to make on My birthday.

00:15:21.224 --> 00:15:23.846
Thank you very much!
